Cloud Bundy, cloud drinking, and so on, the beginning of the year of the rat brain war.

Under the epidemic, "grow up" friends never idle, although temporarily imprisoned feet, but does not affect have an interesting soul.

Internet users entertain themselves at home in a variety of ways. Some people are too busy to panic in their fish tank fishing up the fish, not enough height also moved to the home ladder; some people regularly live broadcast daily brushing teeth also live broadcast sleep. In a near-still scene of a live performance art scene, 18.5 million people gathered to watch.

From the beginning of the new year, you can easily think of cloud gathering, cloud drinking, cloud Bundy, there are also sad with a bit of funny cloud supervisor, cloud dating, Cloud House, and even some people seriously proposed cloud wedding.

Some people get poetry and far-off gratification from "cloud hi" (getting high online) , creating the conditions for normal life and socializing during the epidemic. Others see more possibilities for online life, and some commercial ventures are starting to emerge. Offline businesses are shuttered, but people's entertainment needs aren't going away, and repression will find a way to find an outlet.

The cloud hi campaign, which began in 2020 with the outbreak isolated at home, is only the beginning of what is best known as cloud disco... You'll find that the longer people stay, the more variety...

When you learn about the activities that used to be done offline, but now seamlessly connect online, you might be able to stay home for another two months.

Cloud dance

Let us swing the "cloud disco" has become the most hi "nerd mode" , this bar by TAXX set off a disco storm, the success of stimulating countless young people and their wallets. In the studio, the DJ is playing the disc coolly, and the young people on the other side of the phone are immersed in the excitement of the music. On Taobao, many family disco tools are sold out of goods.

The first "Cloud Disco" by Changsha brand Mr. Shi San Sir TEEN opened less than half an hour with 300,000 fans; the Third One bar was streaming live for five hours with a total of more than 1.21 million people online, receiving more than 2 million tips.

Epidemic hit, the line of entertainment to press the pause button, "live" as the support of the "cloud Bundy" , but bars, nightclubs and other line entertainment opened up a new scene.

Clouds drink wine

Cloud drinking, as the name implies, is the non-line under the liquor bureau. Several people raise a glass together, open group chat video, in front of the computer, mobile phone screen cheers. It's a game of rock-paper-scissors. It's a game of chance.

You can't leave the house, but you can't let your feelings get in the way. Whether you are in the first-tier cities of Shangguang in the north, in the remote countryside, or in Wuhan is fighting the front line of the epidemic, through the mobile phone can bring everyone back together. Instead, the epidemic has become a catalyst, in the boring and even depressing days, so that the network "cloud life" has some fun. Usually, be in a different place, how does a few brothers have the opportunity to sit together?

After a netizen stays at home for three days, can not sit still finally, organized other 5 small partners, launched the first year of the rat cloud drinking activity. The event was an unprecedented success, and two hours later, he began organizing a second one, another round..

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Cloud dinner

What about people who don't drink? It's okay. We can still have dinner together

There's nothing worse than sitting at home and eating food. Especially those who rely on hot pot, barbecue, milk tea life. Milk tea can also take away, one of the hot pot to eat how hard it?

Cloud dinner, the first in the WECHAT group across the air battle map, originally used to stimulate late at night to tease those friends who lose weight.

And now it's everyone's comfort. Others made improvements, organizing small groups of people to eat up. Turn on the video, eat at home, and talk while you eat. Buy a beer, grab a pair of Chopsticks, open Wechat, you can gather a wave. Hot Pot, roast, milk tea, minutes were arranged.

Li Ting and his family, who have been cut off by the outbreak, have made cloud dinners a daily routine; Wang Yang's father and a group of aunts and uncles have arranged to have them every day at 5:30 Sharp, with dinner in front of the camera first, after the introductions. What you don't know is that cloud dinners have become a new hobby for middle-aged and elderly people. Before there is square dancing, the existing clouds gather for dinner.

But Wang Yang's mother strongly rejected the idea. For the sake of her husband's face, she has to rack her brains every day to renovate the dishes. Wang Yang recently discovered that their cloud dinner was about to become earthy.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Clouds sleep

And "Cloud Bundy" , "cloud sleep" is also in the overnight fire. In less than three hours, 2.35 million people poured into the booth. Recently, Douyin Blogger "whose round three" went viral because of the live broadcast, with 18.5 million users at most watching his sleeping position at the same time, 39,000 of them painting gifts for him.

"whose round three" admitted that he also has love trouble, 5 pm, fans urged him to go to bed, and some people therefore "threatened" he did not go to bed on clearance. Even get up to the toilet, drinking water will be criticized irresponsible, you can imagine, we are how much like to see him sleep. What's the fun of going to bed live? He's weird, too.

"I went to bed live because I was bored, but I didn't think you were more bored than me, from 1 to 4. It turns out you can make money sleeping in bed doing nothing. "

This is the standard sense of lying earned ah, even sublimated to "sleep earned. ". Those of you watching him sleep, aren't you sleepy? Don't you just feel better scrubbing presents at night? How are you GONNA get up for a cloud conference the next day?

Cloud dance

Stay at home, bitter young people, bitter family dog, but also bitter like dancing in the crowd of parents. What if there's no square? What if we don't have a ballroom or an old people's Club? Someone's having a cloud dance at home. In the living room, parents hold each other's waists, mobile phones on the table, wechat open group video, two people dance while watching the video on the other side, several pairs of dancing uncle, aunt, really envy their ability to amuse themselves.

If, parents found a multi-party video APP, dozens of video can be accessed at the same time free, square dance can walk up? I'm sorry about your living room.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Cloud Gym

You can do pe at home? In order to let the children at home from school can exercise, physical education teachers are also broken heart.

A middle school in Hangzhou has launched a new set of cloud physical education classes on nails. Physical Education Teachers have come up with many fun ways to teach, such as playing ice hockey at home with slippers, and jumping high at home with cardboard. Slippers... well... may require a very good quality. When the gym teacher became an anchor, it was so much fun to be home.

Even Olympic champion Yang Wei has recently joined the sport for all. What you think of as a cloud gym class: feel the fish, paddle, and move around. In fact, the real is: champion-grade Trolley, goose-style balance, high-difficulty vertical fork. Of course, there are more square style. Physical Education teacher a person in front of the air and the camera warm-up, in front of a screen children's chaos dance, want to correct and can not reach, ask Physical Education Teacher Psychological Shadow area..

Friendly Tip: Please do not love such a physical education!

Cloud, raise the flag

The young people in the home in cloud dance, middle-aged and elderly in the cloud drink, cloud dance, children can have what cloud entertainment?

Be Serious. The pupils have started school.

Facing the beginning of the school season, children not only did not delay learning, even raising the flag can also be completed at home. When the national anthem sounded, the whole school at home through the network to participate in the flag-raising ceremony. The children are still wearing a red scarf, wearing school uniforms, the national anthem sounded, Young Pioneers across the screen, standing, line of Young Pioneers ceremony, did not join the team of students line of attention.

Well, it looks like it. I'm impressed.

Cloud supervisor

In 2020, the strongest "excavator team" was born, Wuhan Huoshen Mountain, Raytheon Mountain base of the construction of live broadcast, fire YTHT.

In the live broadcast of two hospitals in Wuhan, a large number of netizens in the comment area gave the construction site a nickname for a sudden whim. A row of white houses is named Hall of Supreme Harmony, and six houses, side by side behind Hall of Supreme Harmony, are called "six doors" . The most popular is a group of diggers, the color of the blue diggers become the tools of the face of the "blue forget machine" , a compact excavator is "little yellow" . And brother Red Bull and putrid mud. CCTV also opened a help list for these excavators.

Different construction equipment also has fans, netizens are happy to use a familiar discourse system to participate in the live broadcast and discussion. "Xiao Huang, mother loves you! " , "digging machine Xiao Lan, not afraid of difficulties" , "forklift Xiao Huang, the pillar of the country" , the rice ring slogan use of no conflict with the feeling.

With its slow tempo, lack of conflict and lack of drama, what drew the crowd of ten million? Perhaps a sense of healing, although there are many people did not go to the front line, but watching the live broadcast, there is always a sense of security. Let's go! Forget the blue machine!

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Cloud Zoo

Of course, zoos around the world can not open their doors, but it does not affect the smart zoo "business. ".

Beijing Zoo, Beijing Wildlife Park recently launched the "online zoo. ". Staff will shoot short videos of the animals'daily lives, as well as live broadcasts of popular animals (see who's the hottest?) . Nantong Forest Wildlife Park and Dongguan City Zoo will also update short video platforms, such as Douyin, where keepers and animals work daily. The Baby Lion, with its creamy voice, was a little Simba in the keeper's arms.

Best of all, the animals were photographed daily with funny background music and subtitles, many animals in the road never to return, and some have accumulated a number of their own iron fans.

Compared with other natural scenic spots, zoos and animal theme parks face different operating pressure. After the park is closed, it is still necessary to ensure the feeding, daily care, disinfection and epidemic prevention of animals in the park, so it is difficult to reduce costs. And opening an online zoo can use this to accumulate popularity, the formation of new consumption point. In addition to live reward, for the future opening of the park to pave the way, the zoo can also therefore reserve the source of visitors, build through Ip, develop derivatives, extend the industrial chain.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Cloud Ginseng conference

We're halfway through February. Doesn't everyone feel like something's missing? Yes, the press conference! Every spring is the time when new phones are released in droves. This year is more special, offline conference can not be held, so, millet took the lead in the online conference (Reebs is indeed Reebs) . In the studio, Lei Jun wore a mask to recommend the new Mi 10. In order not to make the live broadcast appear awkward, the live broadcast room also specially added some applause sound effects to foil the live broadcast atmosphere. How do I know that? Lei Jun said so himself.

Although it is an online conference, the heat is no less than the offline release, who knows how many people to attend the conference playing mobile phones, active choice to watch the live broadcast is really quite a lot will listen carefully, the whole live broadcast has received more than 1.16 million people to watch. At the cloud event, fans can also interact in real time with the live stream of the brand and buy more as they watch.

Compared with the traditional offline conference, the cloud conference not only avoids the risk of a large number of people gathering, but also saves the venue and manpower cost. Taobao live said that the future will be such a "cloud conference" model to promote more businesses. Would you rather watch an online press conference?

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
People want to "cloud hi" , because the epidemic led to stay at home for a long time to fall into the boring. Things that normally don't matter now have the power to kill time and anxiety. There is a very interesting topic on micro-blog, called "like me at home very badly, " how boring can stay at home?

Invent Super Mix, Mix any two ingredients in your home and Cook until you're satisfied; paint your face with flour and paint, then pull out your scarf and use it as a water sleeve; cut your hair for as long as you want; In the middle of the night, Liu secretly went downstairs and made a snowman. At two o'clock in the morning, he took photos of the first rain in Beijing in 2020

In recent days, many friends around said that they would take the opportunity to run in the snow for two minutes, happy as a dog; many friends said that after the "release" the first thing is to go to Haidilao to eat; A friend said a whole holiday cooking long, at least the kitchen smoke alarm never sounded. People are really choked up, a retaliatory spending seems to be unavoidable. What about you? What do you want to do after the outbreak?
